WEBVTT

00:04:59.086 --> 00:05:04.879
into something that every single person
can understand, use and shape.

00:05:06.376 --> 00:05:10.128
Lawyers are crucial
in that fight, no doubt,

00:05:10.152 --> 00:05:12.082
but we can't leave it to lawyers alone.

00:05:13.147 --> 00:05:15.448
In health care, for example,

00:05:15.472 --> 00:05:18.825
we don't just rely
on doctors to serve patients.

00:05:18.849 --> 00:05:23.055
We have nurses and midwives
and community health workers.

00:05:23.925 --> 00:05:26.830
The same should be true of justice.

00:05:27.767 --> 00:05:29.791
Community legal workers,

00:05:29.815 --> 00:05:32.220
sometimes we call them
community paralegals,